Package agent

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAgent
    Interface for a mobile agent capable of arriving at agent servers and executing tasks.
    IAgentServer
    Interface for an agent server which can order agents to migrate and track visited agent history.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    Represents a mobile agent capable of finding servers, migrating to them, and executing tasks.
    AgentClient
    Represents a complete mobile, networked agent capable of sending the agent to servers and waiting for it to return.
    AgentHandler
    Socket handler for managing incoming Agents.
    AgentServer
    An agent server accepts TCP socket connections on a server port to receive agents.
